  ## EventCancelRequest (1) -> Esto nos sirve?? ❓
  
  - GET /api/v1/EventCancelRequest/{OrgCode}/{EventID}
      
      - summary: Basic - Get a single EventCancelRequest by its parameters.
          
          The purpose of this endpoint is to be able to _cancel_ an event when an Event Cancel Request has been submitted
          
          i.e. through the OSB My Events page
          
          ((If you wish to cancel an event, do it through a Edit (PUT) Event call using ReasonPhrase))
          
      - requiredPath: OrgCode:string, EventID:integer
          
      - responseCodes: 200
          
  
